 Technically, you an cover that in UI design as well, but traditionally most

26
00:01:15,730 --> 00:01:19,930
 of the UI design classes I see focus on on-screen interaction.

27
00:01:19,930 --> 00:01:22,900
 In HCI, we'll talk about the more general methods that apply to

28
